      "role": "user",
      "content": "the support doesn't really change the fact that he's gone. it just makes the silence louder. i look at his side of the bed and i just feel like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. it feels like i'm just performing the motions of a person, but there's nobody actually home anymore. why am i even trying to \"get through\" it when there's nothing to get through to?",
