      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to be \"gentle\" with myself when everything feels so broken. i look at the empty space next to me and it feels like half of my soul was ripped out. it's like i'm just a shadow lingering in a house that doesn't want me here anymore. if the person who made this life worth living is gone, then what's the point of me staying here in the dark? it feels like i'm just holding on to a ghost of a life that ended a long time ago.",
